# ğŸŒ¦ï¸ Weather & News Dashboard (API Integration Project)

A modern multi-page dashboard application that integrates **Weather API** and **News API** to provide real-time weather updates, 5-day forecasts, and the latest news headlines.

Built using **React (Frontend)** with live **REST API integration**, this project demonstrates asynchronous data fetching, routing, state management, and responsive UI design.

